    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Cocktails with Canapes\nBourbon • Scotch • Canadian • Blended Whiskey\nMartini-mixed to your own taste with:\nGin • Vodka\nBloody Mary • Daiquiri\nManhattan • Whiskey Sour\nAperitif Wine • Sherry • Gin and Tonic\nMichelob Beer • Tomato Juice • Soft Drinks\nService is limited to two drinks per passenger.\nMenu\nAppetizer\nTo Tease Your Palate\nSalad\nCrisp Garden Greens\nWith Classic Dressing\nEntrees\nRoast Sirloin of Beef\nVeal Chop Wisconsin\nCarved from the Cart\nMilk-Fed Veal, Flavored\nand Served with Natural Juices\nwith Old-Fashioned Stuffing\nRedwood Forest Game Hen\nRoasted and Topped with Bing Cherry Sauce,\nPresented with Rice Pilaff\nA Selection of Vegetables\nSPECIALLY SELECTED WINES\nDessert\nSelections from the Cart\nCoffee\nTea\nMilk\nChildren's Meals Are Also Available: Cheeseburger-Frankfurter-Fried Chicken\nBrandies and Liqueurs\nCognac V.S.O.P. • Creme de Menthe • Drambuie\nBenedictine \u0026 Brandy • Grand Marnier • Coffee Liqueur\nWeare so glad you could join us today!\nAA Form 1349-1\ncrimee in v.o.A"
